                "caption": "Figure 1:Pinductorarchitecture overview.Given a small set of offline observation-action trajectories and an environment description, an LLM proposes a POMDP world model in code (dashed arrows). The resulting model is used for filtering and planning during environment interaction, and is periodically refined by the LLM to optimize a belief-based likelihood objective (solid arrows).",
