                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.13740/2605.13740v1/x25.png",
                "caption": "Figure 12:Semantic-information ablation.Average episode reward when meaningful environment and object names are replaced with less informative labels. Performance drops across environments, suggesting thatPinductoruses semantic cues as structured priors rather than only fitting trajectories.",
